### 🧪 File Upload HTTP Test Client
# Catatan: Pengetesan upload multipart/form-data via HTTP Client
# membutuhkan file fisik lokal di PC Anda untuk dilampirkan.

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# 1. Upload File Tunggal (Single File)
# Gantilah path 'dummy.png' di bawah dengan path file gambar nyata jika diperlukan
POST {{host}}/api/files/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="dummy.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./dummy.png
--WebAppBoundary--

###

# 2. Upload Multiple Files
POST {{host}}/api/files/upload-multiple
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="dummy1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./dummy.png
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="dummy2.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./dummy.png
--WebAppBoundary--
